CPSequenceVar
Decision variable used to represent a sequence of nodes As an invariant of the domain, the nodes are partitioned into 3 categories: - member ones, which are part of the sequence and ordered - possible ones, which could be part of the sequence - excluded ones, which cannot be part of the sequence The constraints pruning a CPSequenceVar does it by remove insertions points from the CPInsertionVar contained within the sequence or by can exclude them.
